Alex talks about the arrest of a Rochester, New York, woman for recording the police from her property earlier this year and covers increasing incidents of police brutality as law enforcement spins out of control and victimizes the citizenry they are supposedly hired to serve and protect. 

Alex talks with nationally syndicated radio talk show host Lionel who introduced Alex at the Talkers Convention's New Media Seminar held on July 10-11, 2011, in New York.
